d high $M_{20}$ ($>$ -1.4) characterise dynamically\nperturbed systems. We also estimate the X-ray cluster morphological parameters\nin the case of {\\it radio loud} clusters. In excellent agreement with previous\nanalyses we confirm that diffuse intracluster radio sources are associated with\nmajor mergers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Nov 2014 16:50:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-11"}
